ant, has 13+ years of experience.","summary":"Bank of India appoints Smt. Usha Ramsinghani as Company Secretary, replacing Shri Rajesh V. Upadhya.\nRamsinghani, a Science graduate, CAIIB, and Chartered Accountant, has 13+ years of experience.","url":"https://www.bseindia.com/stockinfo/AnnPdfOpen.aspx?Pname=35405a2c-b5de-4090-a912-42450e176b51.pdf","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-01-27T17:02:58","source":"BSE"},{"id":"260125139392380","title":"Corporate credit demand rebounds in Q3, with 13 banks reporting 10.6% YoY growth in lending, up from 8% in Q2.\nPSU and mid-sized banks saw sharper growth; Central Bank of India led with 23.2% YoY growth, followed by RBL at 16.5%.","summary":"Corporate credit demand rebounds in Q3, with 13 banks reporting 10.6% YoY growth in lending, up from 8% in Q2.\nPSU and mid-sized banks saw sharper growth; Central Bank of India led with 23.2% YoY growth, followed by RBL at 16.5%.","url":"https://www.financialexpress.com/business/banking-finance/corporate-credit-begins-to-make-a-comeback-in-q3/4119026/","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-01-25T20:49:00","source":"Financial Express"}]}]